Data_Sources.source_notes: Official Winona State University enrollment counts reported by Institutional Planning, Assessment, and Research (IPAR). Includes program-level enrollment where available. Trend logic: Fall 2020 vs. Fall 2021 enrollment. Small changes (<2 students) are Stable; 5% or greater changes are Up/Down. Zero-to-nonzero changes are treated as Up or Down. Programs with missing enrollment data are excluded from trend classification. This dashboard displays programs currently accepting new students. Programs that are paused or not accepting applications are intentionally excluded.
